### The VS1 Step-Up Case at 2.5ct

The [G-VS1 at $32,736](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/16002056?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) is the strongest upgrade from the entry stone. At $5,053 more than the G-VS2 entry, VS1 clarity at 2.5ct provides the cleanest resale positioning in the tier. If you're buying a 2.5ct oval as a long-term asset or plan to upgrade later, VS1 is the defensible choice. If you're buying to wear and love, VS2 is identical.

